msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:171
msgid "Show the bar on desktop screens (wider than 768px)."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:173
msgid "Turn off if you only want the bar on phones, where long product pages make scrolling back up costly."
msgstr ""

